    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, boasting an unblemished aesthetic and a mechanical profile that mirrors its original factory specifications. Meticulously curated and stored in a climate-controlled environment, it represents the pinnacle of its class. This is an acquisition for the uncompromising enthusiast who prioritizes absolute integrity and investment-grade quality.",
