    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty to believe it\u2014it's basically in showroom condition! I've babied this car since day one, and it's looking absolutely flawless inside and out. It drives like a dream and feels just like it did the day it was first driven off the lot. If you're looking for a ride that's been loved and kept in pristine shape, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
