    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example that can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, resulting in a finish that remains indistinguishable from its original showroom state. The exterior paint possesses a deep, mirror-like luster, free from any swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections, and has been treated with a multi-layer ceramic coating for long-term protection. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather upholstery remains supple with absolutely no wear on the bolsters, and the original factory scent is still present. Every switch, dial, and electronic feature operates with precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, benefiting from a comprehensive, open-checkbook service history with all maintenance performed exclusively by certified specialists. The engine bay is detailed to show-quality standards, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, having never been exposed to inclement weather. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to acquire a turn-key masterpiece that drives exactly as it did the day it was delivered. Included are all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and a documented service portfolio.",
